B route, Rich.

10:08.240 --> 10:12.239
What, through fucking Helmand?

10:19.840 --> 10:23.319
Well done, Alo. It's a dead end.

10:23.320 --> 10:26.239
Nah, it's fine. I can get round
that. Alo, no.

10:26.240 --> 10:27.439
I can make it.

10:27.440 --> 10:30.599
