were you doing back there?

11:32.520 --> 11:36.519
I don't know, Mini, OK?

11:37.960 --> 11:40.639
Woo-hoo!

11:40.640 --> 11:44.639
- Put a donk on it, people!
- What the fuck is he on?

11:46.360 --> 11:50.359
- Franky?
