12:13.560 --> 12:17.559
Look! It's... it's a freaking angel!

12:17.680 --> 12:18.919
Oh, my God!

12:18.920 --> 12:20.239
Oh, no, it's a car.

12:20.240 --> 12:24.239
Of course it's a fucking car, Nick.

12:26.440 --> 12:27.879
