12:43.440 --> 12:45.799
My angel!

12:45.800 --> 12:48.439
- No, that's an angel.
- Leave the angel alone, Nick.

12:48.440 --> 12:50.079
What direction's it in, man?

12:50.080 --> 12:53.759
Cross country as the crow flies,
about an hour. Veer southwest.

12:53.760 --> 12:56.399
Thank you, my henna-handed honcho.

12:56.400 --> 12:59.959
Fingers!

12:59.960 --> 13:03.959
- Don't worry, dude.
- Everything will be OK.

13:04.320 --> 13:06.879
We'll be there.
Bye, guys.

13:06.880 --> 13:10.439
Have fun, kids.
Bye, honey.

13:10.440 --> 13:13.119
- I won't let you down, man!
- Bye.

13:13.120 --> 13:17.119
Bye.

13:21.440 --> 13:23.319
Maybe they're...

13:23.320 --> 13:27.319
post-apocalyptic savages, that'll eat
them alive and make, like,

13:27.800 --> 13:31.799
pants from their skin
and a fucking glockenspiel
from their bones and shit.

13:31.880 --> 13:34.999
- Shut the fuck up, Nick.
- Southwest.

13:35.000 --> 13:38.999
South... south...

13:42.440 --> 13:44.039
Alo...

13:44.040 --> 13:47.199
A horse shit!

13:47.200 --> 13:51.199
