13:51.680 --> 13:55.679
Once more unto the breach,
my friends.

13:57.000 --> 14:00.639
Now, who's with me?!

14:04.960 --> 14:08.959
Hey, Alo, you've got to teach me
that trick, man, with the shit.

14:19.880 --> 14:22.639
Luncheon already?
It's nearly one, David.

14:22.640 --> 14:26.639
How my idle morning has flown.

14:50.080 --> 14:51.879
