15:03.160 --> 15:05.559
Pit stop, you beautiful wankers!

15:05.560 --> 15:08.679
We've only just started, you prick.

15:08.680 --> 15:12.679
One for the road, Mini.

15:18.840 --> 15:22.839
Beer rain! There is a God!

15:40.560 --> 15:42.399
What the fuck was that for?

15:42.400 --> 15:44.239
