to get to,

15:44.240 --> 15:46.919
Mr I Don't Give A Fuck
About Anything Or Anyone.

15:46.920 --> 15:50.919
- You're wrong, I do.
- What about our agreement?

15:53.760 --> 15:55.359
Mini?

15:55.360 --> 15:58.799
- What agreement?
- You deserve better, remember?

15:58.800 --> 16:01.239
Have you been saying shit
behind my back?

16:01.240 --> 16:04.639
