16:08.960 --> 16:10.679
I'll see you at the church.

16:10.680 --> 16:13.239
No, no, no, we can't split up.

16:13.240 --> 16:14.719
I can get us there, I promise.

16:16.160 --> 16:19.199
Come with us. If you like.

16:19.200 --> 16:22.239
No way! She's staying right here.

16:22.240 --> 16:26.239
Come on, Franky.

16:28.280 --> 16:32.279
Franky, I... I'm trying
to protect you.

16:33.360 --> 16:35.599
Mini, I'll see you later, OK?

16:35.600 --> 16:38.679
He just wants to fuck you
and then fuck you up!

16:38.680 --> 16:42.679
