16:49.640 --> 16:51.919
So you put an insect thingy on her?

16:51.920 --> 16:54.519
A bug. We'll catch her soon enough.

16:54.520 --> 16:56.239
She isn't a dog, David.

16:56.240 --> 17:00.239
Could you unwrap another Werther's
for me, please, Sonia?

17:08.920 --> 17:11.159
And each child rings a year
on the tree of our love

17:11.160 --> 17:12.959
we planted on our wedding day.

17:12.960 --> 17:15.679
- How many do you have, Crystal?
- 13.

17:15.680 --> 17:19.679
No more travelling the world
like a scag-injected tumbleweed.

17:21.079 --> 17:24.759
I rooted in the soil
of our marriage.

17:24.760 --> 17:27.559
- Diesel was a roadie.
- Oh, really? Who for?

17:27.560 --> 17:31.559
Throbbing Gristle, er, Alien Sex
Fiend, er... Napalm Death...

17:31.600 --> 17:32.959
No fucking way!

17:32.960 --> 17:36.639
Way, way wayward,
spiritually bereft.

17:36.640 --> 17:38.879
Bullshit.

17:38.880 --> 17:41.079
Now I hunter-gather!

17:41.080 --> 17:45.079
