and I... and I can't stop it now.

18:16.680 --> 18:20.559
Well, if anyone can, McGuinness can.

18:20.560 --> 18:24.559
Go... or you'll regret it.

18:24.720 --> 18:28.679
Slide off me, sweatbox.

18:28.680 --> 18:31.559
