25:38.080 --> 25:42.079
Aaah!

25:42.800 --> 25:46.799
Like serpents coiled
in perpetual yin-yang mating.

25:47.480 --> 25:51.399
Spiritual Siamese twins
with male-to-female body parts.

25:51.400 --> 25:53.359
Your lives are one.

25:53.360 --> 25:55.719
My key fits her lock.

25:55.720 --> 25:57.799
