my ear.

25:57.800 --> 26:00.599
To hear the glory of our
union!

26:00.600 --> 26:02.679
Slit my wrists now.

26:02.680 --> 26:03.719
What?

26:03.720 --> 26:04.759
Not long before...

26:04.760 --> 26:08.759
