26:08.760 --> 26:11.799
Ace.

26:11.800 --> 26:13.999
Go on without me!

26:14.000 --> 26:15.959
I'll die here alone.
It's all I deserve.

26:15.960 --> 26:18.399
Just keep your leg still, all right?
You're in a rabbit snare.

26:18.400 --> 26:21.639
Ow! Save yourself
andleave me to the bears!

26:21.640 --> 26:25.039
We're in Somerset, Nick!

26:25.040 --> 26:26.719
To the fucking squirrels, then!

26:26.720 --> 26:28.359
Ah!

26:28.360 --> 26:31.319
- Go!
- Just shut up, all right?

26:31.320 --> 26:35.319
Shut up and keep your frigging leg
still!

26:40.480 --> 26:42.759
Oh, bloody hell, Nick!

26:42.760 --> 26:44.879
- When did you last change these?!
- It's not them.

26:44.880 --> 26:47.159
That's the smell of a loser's death.

26:47.160 --> 26:49.039
You're not a loser.

26:49.040 --> 26:52.039
You're a bit of a prick,

26:52.040 --> 26:56.039
but peel away that prick...
and there's a good man in there.

26:56.120 --> 26:59.639
- Come on, big boy!
- No... No!

26:59.640 --> 27:02.959
- Arise, sire!
- Argh!

27:02.960 --> 27:05.719
My beer. I want my beer.

27:05.720 --> 27:08.879
No, let it go.

27:08.880 --> 27:12.879
- You're a good... good bloke, Alo.
- Yeah, I know.

27:20.120 --> 27:24.119
Liv!

27:29.840 --> 27:32.519
Where is, er... everyone else?

27:32.520 --> 27:34.399
Like Franky?

27:34.400 --> 27:38.399
