- They'll be here.
- You reckon?

28:59.120 --> 29:01.799
They have to be -
they're our friends, Rich.

29:01.800 --> 29:05.799
Let's just find two people
for, like, backup.

29:10.960 --> 29:14.959
Two people - easy.

29:23.600 --> 29:26.919
Oh, my God!

29:26.920 --> 29:29.239
- Come on!
- We're gonna live!

29:29.240 --> 29:31.319
- A road!
- We're gonna live!

29:31.320 --> 29:32.399
We're saved!

29:32.400 --> 29:34.399
But there's loads of room!

29:34.400 --> 29:38.399
Oh, very salubrious, Bertie.

29:40.720 --> 29:42.719
- Er, hi.
- Oh, hello, lad.

29:42.720 --> 29:44.479
Will you be here in an hour?

29:44.480 --> 29:48.479
- Oh, can't say!
- We've not got long.

29:49.480 --> 29:53.119
Oh, yeah, good one.
No way.

29:53.120 --> 29:56.079
We need two witnesses
so we can get married,

29:56.080 --> 29:59.319
cos everything's gone wrong and...
Please.

29:59.320 --> 30:02.399
Of course, dear, of course.

30:02.400 --> 30:03.839
In an hour, then.

30:03.840 --> 30:05.279
- Yeah.
- Yeah, yeah!

30:05.280 --> 30:09.279
- Yeah. OK.
- Thank you.

30:24.880 --> 30:28.879
Liv?

30:32.440 --> 30:36.439
Matty?

30:40.920 --> 30:42.599
Are you OK?

30:42.600 --> 30:46.599
I'm sorry... I'm sorry, I thought...

30:48.520 --> 30:52.519
Where's Liv?

30:52.920 --> 30:55.319
I tried to stay away from you
and I can't.

30:55.320 --> 30:57.199
Here we are...

30:57.200 --> 31:00.199
It's not random.

31:00.200 --> 31:04.199
You feel it, right?

31:05.240 --> 31:07.599
I really want to fucking kiss you,
but I can't.

31:07.600 --> 31:10.519
Then why are you head-fucking me?!

31:10.520 --> 31:12.719
Franky, don't...

31:12.720 --> 31:16.719
Just as fucked in the head
as you are.

31:18.640 --> 31:20.759
You know, when I was six,

31:20.760 --> 31:24.759
teacher asked me
to think of something beautiful.

31:26.120 --> 31:30.119
I said 9/11.

31:30.520 --> 31:34.519
Saw it on the TV in this care home
with the sound on mute.

31:34.680 --> 31:38.679
Teacher told me how many people
had died.

31:39.400 --> 31:42.199
And all the other kids
in the class cried,

31:42.200 --> 31:46.199
and I knew then that I was...

31:46.280 --> 31:50.279
wrong.

31:51.560 --> 31:53.479
I guess

31:53.480 --> 31:57.479
that's why my parents gave me up.

31:57.480 --> 32:01.039
Because they knew, too...

32:01.040 --> 32:05.039
right from the beginning.

33:22.240 --> 33:26.239
- Franky?
- Get off me. Get off me!

33:30.920 --> 33:34.919
Franky, wait! Franky!

33:36.480 --> 33:40.479
Franky, come back! Franky!

33:40.960 --> 33:43.279
- Please...
- What the hell happened?

33:43.280 --> 33:47.279
What the fuck have you done?

33:47.840 --> 33:51.559
Franky!

33:51.560 --> 33:55.319
Franky, please, come back!

33:55.320 --> 33:59.319
Franky!

34:06.160 --> 34:10.159
Franky!

34:12.320 --> 34:13.918
Franky!

34:21.520 --> 34:23.399
Franky!

34:23.400 --> 34:25.279
Can you see her?

34:25.280 --> 34:29.279
She's here! Franky, hold on!

34:30.400 --> 34:33.079
- Take my hand, Franky.
- Go away.

34:33.080 --> 34:35.958
Please, Franky!

34:35.960 --> 34:37.679
Franky, take my hand!

34:37.679 --> 34:40.599
Franky, please, please!

34:40.600 --> 34:43.478
I'm so sorry, Franky!

34:43.480 --> 34:47.478
Come on, please, take my hand.

34:49.840 --> 34:53.839
OK!

35:02.560 --> 35:06.559
Want a hand?

35:13.320 --> 35:17.319
OK?

35:25.480 --> 35:29.319
Franky... did he...

35:29.320 --> 35:30.479
hurt you?

35:30.480 --> 35:34.479
It's not what it looks like, Liv.
I swear, she just lost it.

35:37.440 --> 35:41.439
I just... wanted to feel...

35:41.640 --> 35:45.639
normal.

35:56.800 --> 35:59.919
Ah!

35:59.920 --> 36:01.879
David fucking Blood!

36:01.880 --> 36:05.879
Shit.

36:06.040 --> 36:10.039
- Oh...
- Oh, fucking...

36:12.040 --> 36:15.999
Hey, stop! Stop! Stop, please!

36:35.200 --> 36:39.199
- They went and got battered.
- They're supposed to be
our friends.

36:39.640 --> 36:41.399
Just us now.

36:41.400 --> 36:44.919
This is so not what I dreamed of.

36:44.920 --> 36:48.399
Why did you cut your lovely hair?

36:48.400 --> 36:52.399
I asked for a trim.

36:52.440 --> 36:56.439
Guess I look the part, I suppose.
Mr and Mrs Mainstream.

36:58.720 --> 37:01.079
Did you actually think
that's what I wanted?

37:01.080 --> 37:03.559
Grace!

37:23.000 --> 37:24.119
Blood is coming!

37:24.120 --> 37:25.759
But my bridesmaids...!

37:25.760 --> 37:29.439
- Nick, do the honours.
- Bring it on.

38:01.000 --> 38:04.039
All we need is love.

38:04.040 --> 38:06.159
Great.

38:06.160 --> 38:07.639
All we need is...

38:07.640 --> 38:09.159
To get on with the service.

38:11.640 --> 38:15.639
Not on God's holy earth.

38:17.760 --> 38:19.159
How did you know I was here?

38:19.160 --> 38:21.199
He put an electric
insect thing on you.

38:21.200 --> 38:23.239
A bug, for the billionth time.

38:23.240 --> 38:25.039
I'm your daughter, not al-Qaeda.

38:25.040 --> 38:26.759
You are coming home with us.

38:28.640 --> 38:29.599
Hey, Grace.

38:29.600 --> 38:33.519
You're all here!

38:33.520 --> 38:36.719
Look at what this motley crew
have done to our little girl.

38:36.720 --> 38:39.319
I'm not your little girl.

38:39.320 --> 38:43.279
Her future's hers, David, not ours.

38:43.280 --> 38:44.839
You...

38:44.840 --> 38:48.839
you corrupters are
all, all, expelled.

38:52.840 --> 38:55.719
You can't do that, sir.

38:55.720 --> 38:59.719
Oh, look how the mighty
have fallen.

39:00.880 --> 39:03.119
Yeah. I fell...

39:03.120 --> 39:06.479
down a f...

39:06.480 --> 39:10.479
reaking k-hole, actually,
but these guys caught me.

39:10.720 --> 39:14.719
It's what mates do.
Cos it's screwed up out there.

39:14.960 --> 39:18.959
I don't know if you've been outside
lately, but it is. But we have a go.

39:19.560 --> 39:23.559
Whatever comes,
we have a good go at it.

39:24.640 --> 39:28.239
Cos it's all we can do.

39:28.240 --> 39:31.599
Right, then, so be it.

39:31.600 --> 39:35.599
But we shall take no further part
in this ridiculous melodrama.

39:43.920 --> 39:47.919
Sonia!

39:51.960 --> 39:54.959
So, are we going to, you know...

39:54.960 --> 39:56.999
get married?

39:57.000 --> 39:59.479
Don't ever cut your hair again.

39:59.480 --> 40:01.439
Not gonna.

40:01.440 --> 40:05.439
It'll grow. You're still my
metal man, my own Tin Man.

40:12.320 --> 40:16.319
So things are good, right, with us?

40:17.280 --> 40:21.279
Yeah. So do we
really need to change things?

40:21.520 --> 40:25.519
You could just take me
to be your boyfriend.

40:26.240 --> 40:30.239
Totally.

40:48.480 --> 40:50.879
I can't walk any more.

40:50.880 --> 40:54.879
Like, ever again.

40:55.320 --> 40:57.639
Hark!

40:57.640 --> 41:01.639
I sense merriment afoot.

41:07.840 --> 41:08.919
Let's go!

41:08.920 --> 41:10.599
Alo!

41:12.120 --> 41:13.599
Oh, please...

41:13.600 --> 41:15.519
Alo!

41:15.520 --> 41:17.119
I can't even walk!

41:17.120 --> 41:21.119
Alo, where the fuck are you going?

41:27.280 --> 41:31.279
Woo-hoo! Woo!

41:39.240 --> 41:40.839
Take a piece of cake.

41:40.840 --> 41:42.199
Take it, take it.

41:55.800 --> 41:59.799
I told you! Yes! Yes!

42:00.440 --> 42:03.759
Ta-da!

42:03.760 --> 42:07.759
OK!

42:17.680 --> 42:21.679
It's not your fault.

42:22.720 --> 42:25.319
We had a good day, didn't we?

42:25.320 --> 42:26.239
What?

42:26.240 --> 42:30.239
The day we met.

42:31.480 --> 42:35.479
I don't want to fuck
with that memory any more.

42:43.760 --> 42:47.359
Let's just...

42:47.360 --> 42:51.359
