43:22.120 --> 43:25.079
Are you OK?

43:25.080 --> 43:26.639
I used to...

43:26.640 --> 43:28.719
beam myself away,

43:28.720 --> 43:30.919
go somewhere in my head

43:30.920 --> 43:33.679
where I felt less...

43:33.680 --> 43:35.999
